==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Built
<hw>Built</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Formed; shaped; constructed; made; --
often used in composition and preceded by the word denoting the form;
<as>as, frigate-<ex>built</ex>, clipper-<ex>built</ex>,
etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Like the generality of Genoese countrywomen, strongly
<qex>built</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Landor.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>buirdly</ent>⟦br⟧
